data.description: HOME SWEET HOME!!!  This home sits on a beautiful spacious front and back level lot. Ranch buyers will love this home with all the wide openings throughout the majority of the house. With a fully renovated kitchen, that hosts brand new white cabinets still in the plastic. granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a brand-new ventilation hood to be installed with the backsplash, any buyer would love to cook in this space. This home has 2 nice-sized secondary bedrooms with large closets and double windows that boast an abundance of natural light. The owner's suite is grand and so is the huge organized closet. Vaulted ceilings in the owner's suite as well as the family room that also has a fireplace. Brand new flooring throughout the kitchen, family room, owner's suite, and a secondary bedroom.Situated in highly sought out Mcdonough Ga. this home is within walking distance of shopping restaurants and family entertainment. The sellers are highly motivated to sell so come with offers ready to close! Sellers concession is available. Preferred closing attorney iis Kimbrough Law & Associates.
